s":{"custom_liquid":"<div class=\"container-jonathan\">\n    <img class=\"img-1\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0888\/3594\/8829\/files\/Jonathan_1.webp?v=1733737553\" alt=\"\">\n    <h2>Jonathan Tah stars in MCM x European Championship 2024 Capsule Collection as our next MCM Maverick.<\/h2>\n    <p> “Nobody can outwork me.” Jonathan Tah was born a Maverick, nothing can stop him. He knows what he is capable of,\n        and the whole world is about to see as he represents Germany in the 2024 Euro football\n        tournament.<br><br><i><strong>“Everybody can choose their own way – and this is good.”<\/strong><\/i><br><br>The\n        perfect face for our Capsule Collection – a relentless champion who always stays true to himself. We love Tah’s\n        power, precision, style, and are honored to call him our latest Maverick. <\/p>\n    <img class=\"img-2\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0888\/3594\/8829\/files\/Jonathan_2.webp?v=1733737553\" alt=\"\">\n    <p class=\" text-3\"> The capsule features pieces designed to elevate your fan game, meticulously crafted and\n        sport inspired. Apparel and bags in classic black and cognac Visetos – sporty essentials leveled up. <\/p>\n    <div class=\"row\">\n        <img class=\"img-3\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0888\/3594\/8829\/files\/Jonathan_3.webp?v=1733737553\" alt=\"\">\n        <img class=\"img-4\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0888\/3594\/8829\/files\/Jonathan_4.webp?v=1733737553\" alt=\"\">\n    <\/div>\n    <p class=\" align-left\"> As well as six special-edition national team Stark Backpacks – just like the ones that\n        brought luck to some of the most important players that MCM has equipped with in the past from Germany, France,\n        Switzerland, Portugal, Korea, and Brazil. The special edition backpacks are available only in Europe, while 200\n        limited edition MCM footballs make this capsule beyond unique globally. <\/p>\n    <img class=\"img-5\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0888\/3594\/8829\/files\/Jonathan_5.webp?v=1733737553\" alt=\"\">\n    <p class=\" text-4\"> Discover the full capsule collection and capture the spirit of this season's most exciting\n        event.<br><br><a href=\"https:\/\/us.mcmworldwide.com\/en_US\/search?cgid=men-new-arrivals\" title=\"search\"><span\n                class=\"bold\"><u>Shop MCM x European Championship 2024 Capsule Collection<\/u><\/span>\n        <\/a><br><br><br>Starring: Jonathan Tah<br>Photographer: Davit Giorgadze<br>Stylist: Christian\n        Stemmler<br>Grooming: Dushan Petrovich <\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n\n<style>\n.container-jonathan {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  align-items: center;\n}\nimg.img-1 {\n  width: 60vw;\n}\n.container-jonathan h2 {\n  font-size: 36px;\n  font-family: \"MCM Favorit Bold Extended\";\n  font-weight: 700;\n  width: 45%;\n  line-height: 48px;\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n  margin-top: 15vh;\n}\n.container-jonathan p {\n  font-family: \"MCM Favorit Variable\";\n  font-size: 14px;\n  line-height: 24px;\n  width: 44%;\n  margin-bottom: 20vh;\n}\np.align-left {\n  margin: 15vh 0;\n}\n.row {\n  display: flex;\n  gap: 51px;\n  padding: 0 91px;\n}\nimg.img-4,\nimg.img-3 {\n  width: 50%;\n}\np.text-3 {\n  margin: 15vh 0;\n}\nimg.img-2 {\n    width: 75vw;\n}\np.text-4 {\n    margin-top: 15vh;\n}\n\n<\/style>"}}},"order":["main","custom_liquid_PTVQyx","custom_liquid_YhkAB6"]}